| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1802 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5ce2fb7f-54a4-5d8f-84bc-577b3854a8da"
